### Synchronous Route Definitions with Plugin Wrapping (Fastify)

Source: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Guides/Migration-Guide-V4.md

Demonstrates refactoring route definitions to use synchronous registration by wrapping routes in a plugin. This improves error reporting and is the recommended approach when using onRoute hooks in plugins.

```javascript
fastify.register((instance, opts, done) => {
  instance.addHook('onRoute', (routeOptions) => {
    const { path, method } = routeOptions;
    console.log({ path, method });
    done();
  });
});

fastify.get('/', (request, reply) => { reply.send('hello') });
```

